### Create account for a customer
POST http://localhost:8080/create/account/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic YWRtaW46YWRtaW4xMjM0

{
  "customerName": "Sara Mohammadi",
  "nationalId": "1111222234",
  "birthDate": "1992-03-20T00:00:00.000Z",
  "customerType": "NATURALPERSION",
  "phoneNumber": "09111222233",
  "address": "Isfahan, Chahar Bagh Street",
  "postalCode": "8173654321"
}

### change the account date ( name, customer type, phone number, address, postal code, account status)
PUT http://localhost:8080/create/account/1111222234
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic YWRtaW46YWRtaW4xMjM0

{
  "customerName": "Sara Mohammadi Updated",
  "nationalId": "1111222234",
  "birthDate": "1992-03-20T00:00:00.000Z",
  "customerType": "LEGALPERSON",
  "phoneNumber": "09999888777",
  "address": "Isfahan, New Address, Enghelab Street",
  "postalCode": "8173111112",
  "accountStatus": "BLOCKED"
}


